--- In nbwrpg@y..., robertdahl <rdahl@t...> wrote:
> Wildrider leaps out of Astrotrain, landind crouched on the ground. 
"Ha
> ha ahah, come out come out wherever you are." he yelled, as he 
raised
> his gun, and pulled the trigger sending a stream of lasers into the 
air.
> He then aimed at the ship, and sent a stream heading towards it, 
then
> another behind him.

    Domnijoe, who had been standing beside the ship, cautiously moved 
forward. She didn't want to be hit by the seemingly random, but 
exuberant lazer fire. She smirked widely as she approached.
    "Weeeellll....you finally arrived." She said, wary. She turned 
to face the re-opening  shuttle door. Blindchaos was in his 
animalistic form, ready for battle. Apparently he feared a trap.
 "That's Blindchaos." she said, jabbing her thumb in her shipmate's 
direction. "If you can put up with his stupid grinning, yer one up on 
me." She clanged her chest in a gruff but friendly greeting. "My 
nick's Domnijoe. Now that you're here, what's next?"
